IPR-ENERGY IDENTITY: FINDING THE CORRECT FORMULA
======================================================================

--- PART 1: PARSEVAL IDENTITIES ---
sum |S_hat(k)|^2 = p*m  (Parseval)
sum |S_hat(k)|^4 = p*E(S)  (4th moment = energy)
