--- PART 2: THREE IPR FORMULAS ---
IPR_all = E(S) / (p*m^2)
IPR_k>0 = (p*E(S) - m^4) / (m(p-m))^2
IPR_direct = sum|S_hat|^4 / (sum|S_hat|^2)^2

